title: NFL ATL: Breaking down Kaepernick’s contract, best free agents
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Breaking down Kaepernick’s contract, best free agents
description:
A room full of heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- breaks down Colin Kaepernick’s six-year contract extension with the San Francisco 49ers.  Elsewhere, as always, the gang takes a look at all of the latest headlines around the league and continues its offseason analysis of free agency.
